subject: Whats your favourite example to demonstrate Test Driven Development

messageBody:
At long last I'm giving a tutorial on test driven development on
Wednesday and am looking for some interesting examples to demo test
driven development. In 10-15 minutes what do you try and build? Any
reason you choose it? Anything in particular you try to demonstrate?

With apologies if you see this posting twice - my gmail account is
getting caught in yahoo's aggressive spam filter. Given the time
sensitive nature of this question I'm reposting via the web interface.

Cheers
Mark Levison
